&lt;p&gt;SE Ranking, an all-in-one SEO and digital marketing platform, is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Design Lead&lt;/strong&gt; to lead design across our SEO Solutions area. We are looking for a design leader who can define a clear product design vision, scale a strong team, and turn complex data-heavy workflows into cohesive, measurable experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will report directly to &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/mikhailkar/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mike Korenugin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and lead Product Design across SEO Solutions - overseeing SEO &amp;amp; AI Search needs of customers across the SE Ranking platform, SE Visible, and Data Product initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In your day-to-day work, you will partner closely with your design team - &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/vdzuman/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vadym Dziuman&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/agarbovski/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Aliaksei Harbouski&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/daria-peresetskaya/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Daria Peresetskaya&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/anastasiya-zhabrun/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Anastasiya Zhabrun&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; - supporting their growth, raising quality standards, and stepping in hands-on when needed to lead by example.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will also collaborate tightly with &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/denisdudinski/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dzianis Dudzinski&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and all PMs/EMs to shape solutions early, balance trade-offs, and ensure design decisions are grounded in product metrics and customer needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a purely managerial role. We expect you to combine &lt;strong&gt;strategic ownership, team leadership, and strong hands-on product design capability.&lt;/strong&gt; You will define and drive the &lt;strong&gt;design vision&lt;/strong&gt; across products, ensuring a shared design language and cohesive user experience as our ecosystem evolves.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Initial Focus Areas:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the first 90 days we expect you to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Define the early draft design vision for SEO Solutions:&lt;/strong&gt; clarify principles and direction that align SE Ranking, SE Visible, and Data initiatives under one coherent design language.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assess team structure:&lt;/strong&gt; identify gaps and set performance standards across the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build a plan (and hopefully start implementing some of it):&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Increase design team productivity:&lt;/strong&gt; optimize collaboration rituals, introduce AI-assisted workflows where valuable, and reduce friction between Design, PM, and Engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strengthen design as the voice of the customer:&lt;/strong&gt; embed research practices, improve validation loops, and ensure UX decisions are grounded in real user behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Align design decisions with data:&lt;/strong&gt; define and reinforce how design outcomes connect to product metrics and business impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Upgrade the design system:&lt;/strong&gt; assess current maturity, improve scalability, patterns, and consistency across data-heavy workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
