&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Performance Marketing Lead to architect our global acquisition engine. This isn’t a role for a traditional &quot;manager&quot;—we need a growth architect who builds, breaks, and innovates. Leveraging an AI-first workflow, you will move faster and scrappier than a standard PPC team to drive quality growth across Google, LinkedIn, and beyond. You’ll own the full strategy-to-execution loop, managing a lean team of specialists to deliver high-intent pipeline and new MRR.&lt;/p&gt;
