&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High-Velocity Experimentation:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and manage a relentless testing engine. You will constantly innovate across creative, landing pages, and bidding strategies, viewing every campaign as a scientific experiment with a clear hypothesis and measurable outcome.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Workflows &amp;amp; Automations:&lt;/strong&gt; Implement and maintain automated workflows (using n8n, Make, Claude, or custom scripts) to handle the mundane. You will leverage AI to automate reporting, creative testing, and bid management, freeing your time for high-level innovation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data &amp;amp; Tracking Architecture:&lt;/strong&gt; Take full ownership of the conversion tracking stack. Ensure the data feeding our algorithms is clean and verified by collaborating with engineering and data teams to implement advanced tracking (CAPI, offline conversions, and server-side tagging).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
