&lt;p&gt;SE Ranking, an all-in-one SEO and digital marketing platform, is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to own the quality of the data our customers trust every day and to evolve our &lt;strong&gt;Local Marketing&lt;/strong&gt; suite — while laying the groundwork for in-app &lt;strong&gt;AI agents&lt;/strong&gt; that help SEO professionals get their work done faster. Do you get excited about turning messy, large-scale data into something customers rely on, and about shaping how AI will do real SEO work alongside them? Then this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
