&lt;p&gt;SE Ranking is a profitable, global SaaS company helping businesses, agencies, and marketing teams improve their visibility across Search, AI Search, and Social. We serve customers worldwide, operate as a remote-first organization, and are entering our next stage of growth as we evolve into an AI-native, multi-product platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a VP Finance to join our leadership team and become the CEO’s partner on financial planning, business performance, capital allocation, long-term value creation, and leadership of the company’s Finance and Legal functions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SE Ranking has built a meaningful, growing SaaS business. As we continue scaling and evolving into an AI-native, multi-product platform, finance must evolve from a reporting function into a strategic operating function.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a finance leader who can help shape company strategy, improve decision-making, strengthen planning and forecasting, and build the financial capabilities required for our next stage of growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is the senior finance leadership role at SE Ranking. The successful candidate will lead the Finance function, serve as a key member of the leadership team, and help build the capabilities, team, and operating discipline required to support a significantly larger and more complex business.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for someone with the ambition and capability to lead Finance at SE Ranking for the long term and play a meaningful role in shaping the company’s future.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is not about maintaining the status quo. It is about helping leadership answer questions such as:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Where should we invest for the highest long-term return?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How should we balance growth and profitability?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How do we allocate resources across products, markets, and initiatives?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;What financial outcomes should we expect from major business decisions?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How do we build a company capable of operating successfully at significantly greater scale?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The VP Finance will report directly to the CEO and serve as a member of the leadership team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Performance, Planning &amp;amp; Decision Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the CEO, Board, and leadership team on long-term value creation&lt;/li&gt;
